HEADS AA

START ** READY1 +* SD
READY1 ** TOP ** RR

TOP .@ TOP +* RR
TOP .. DOWN +. DD
DOWN .. BOTTOM ++ RR
BOTTOM @. BOTTOM *+ RR
BOTTOM .. UP .+ UU
UP .. TOP ++ RR

BOTTOM __ TRANSITION1 ** LS
TRANSITION1 ** TRANSITION2 ** DS
TRANSITION2 ** TRANSITION3 ** LL
TRANSITION3 ** TRANSITION4 ++ LL
TRANSITION4 ** LEFT ++ DD

LEFT .@ LEFT +* DD
LEFT .. TOR ++ RR
TOR +. RIGHT ++ DD
RIGHT @. RIGHT @+ DD
RIGHT .. TOL ++ LL
TOL .+ LEFT ++ DD

LEFT __ STOP ** SS
